00:50:50.280 --> 00:50:53.970 align:middle line:84%
Their fate-- an
undignified and cold death.

00:50:53.970 --> 00:51:02.360 align:middle line:90%


00:51:02.360 --> 00:51:07.050 align:middle line:84%
