a pork chop or a schnitzel.

00:52:20.560 --> 00:52:26.800 align:middle line:90%


00:52:26.800 --> 00:52:29.170 align:middle line:90%
And cattle fare no better.

00:52:29.170 --> 00:52:32.320 align:middle line:84%
Many animals spend their
lives in narrow stalls,

00:52:32.320 --> 00:52:34.750 align:middle line:90%
the lucky ones in open pens.

00:52:34.750 --> 00:52:37.090 align:middle line:84%
Many, however, vegetate
in tether stalls.

00:52:37.090 --> 00:52:47.930 align:middle line:90%


00:52:47.930 --> 00:52:50.570 align:middle line:84%
One step forward,
one step backward--

00:52:50.570 --> 00:52:52.790 align:middle line:84%
that is all the freedom
of movement they have.

00:52:52.790 --> 00:52:56.450 align:middle line:90%


00:52:56.450 --> 00:52:58.940 align:middle line:90%
A life expectancy of 30 years--

00:52:58.940 --> 00:53:02.050 align:middle line:84%
that's something industrial-age
cattle can only dream of.

00:53:02.050 --> 00:53:16.430 align:middle line:90%


00:53:16.430 --> 00:53:18.540 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:53:18.540 --> 00:53:51.860 align:middle line:90%


00:53:51.860 --> 00:53:55.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Infections are one of the
biggest problems in factory

00:53:55.310 --> 00:53:56.540 align:middle line:90%
farms.

00:53:56.540 --> 00:54:00.230 align:middle line:84%
