>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:54:28.810 --> 00:54:42.250 align:middle line:90%


00:54:42.250 --> 00:54:46.380 align:middle line:84%
>> The routine and improper use
of antibiotics in factory farms

00:54:46.380 --> 00:54:50.550 align:middle line:84%
presents a big health risk,
not just for the animals,

00:54:50.550 --> 00:54:54.570 align:middle line:84%
because more and more bacteria
strains are becoming resistant,

00:54:54.570 --> 00:54:58.080 align:middle line:84%
