00:55:13.500 --> 00:55:15.600 align:middle line:84%
has become resistant
to antibiotics.

00:55:15.600 --> 00:55:26.240 align:middle line:90%


00:55:26.240 --> 00:55:29.210 align:middle line:84%
But the animals are not
only affected physically.

00:55:29.210 --> 00:55:31.835 align:middle line:84%
Industrial farming harms
them on all levels.

00:55:31.835 --> 00:55:41.390 align:middle line:90%


00:55:41.390 --> 00:55:43.310 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:55:43.310 --> 00:56:15.810 align:middle line:90%


00:56:15.810 --> 00:56:21.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Having once seen pigs in
