00:57:30.990 --> 00:57:34.215 align:middle line:90%
at these horrible factory farms.

00:57:34.215 --> 00:57:45.710 align:middle line:90%


00:57:45.710 --> 00:57:48.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Not only our meat consumption
