01:01:26.264 --> 01:01:37.890 align:middle line:90%


01:01:37.890 --> 01:01:43.620 align:middle line:84%
>> We know in our bones that
harming mothers who are just

01:01:43.620 --> 01:01:46.290 align:middle line:84%
giving birth to babies
