01:01:51.150 --> 01:01:53.310 align:middle line:90%
our own compassion and kindness.

01:01:53.310 --> 01:01:56.707 align:middle line:84%
And so when we're eating animal
foods, eating dairy products,

01:01:56.707 --> 01:01:58.040 align:middle line:90%
